{"title":"Vue背单词项目：打包所遇到的一些问题","uid":"0b445781f040297fc574e33d6ca71b89","slug":"Vue-WordProject2","date":"2020-05-01T01:58:47.000Z","updated":"2020-05-08T06:00:49.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Vue-WordProject2.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200508135620.png","content":"<h2 id=\"VUE打包报UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning问题\"><a href=\"#VUE打包报UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"VUE打包报UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning问题\"></a>VUE打包报<code>UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning</code>问题</h2><ul>\n<li>在build文件夹下的build.js中加入<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">process.on(&#39;unhandledRejection&#39;, (reason, p) &#x3D;&gt; &#123;\n  console.log(&#39;Unhandled Rejection at: Promise&#39;, p, &#39;reason:&#39;, reason);\n  &#x2F;&#x2F; application specific logging, throwing an error, or other logic here\n&#125;);</code></pre>\n<img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200501101019.png\"></li>\n</ul>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h2 id=\"打包后报-Error-postcss-svgo-Error-in-parsing-SVG-Unquoted-attribute-value\"><a href=\"#打包后报-Error-postcss-svgo-Error-in-parsing-SVG-Unquoted-attribute-value\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"打包后报 Error: postcss-svgo: Error in parsing SVG: Unquoted attribute value\"></a>打包后报 <code>Error: postcss-svgo: Error in parsing SVG: Unquoted attribute value</code></h2><ul>\n<li>把用到SVG的地方用双引号包起来</li>\n<li>如mui.css中<br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200501101316.png\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"打包后，打开index-html白屏\"><a href=\"#打包后，打开index-html白屏\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"打包后，打开index.html白屏\"></a>打包后，打开index.html白屏</h2><ul>\n<li>在config文件夹中找到index.js打开,把build下的assetsPublicPath: ‘/‘改成assetsPublicPath: ‘./‘。dev下的不用改</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200501100258.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"打包后跨域访问的问题\"><a href=\"#打包后跨域访问的问题\" class=\